Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就是平常的状态么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是平常的状态啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说这顶帽子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不好看么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发型都变的怪怪的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…越弄越糟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是戴上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平常不戴的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这顶帽子的图案很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图案很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:03:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的回忆还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝啤酒么 啤酒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 你喝点儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长您呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一罐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐你也喝点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一罐就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这桌要一罐啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个关东煮 分量好足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃个鸡蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 你也喝点儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 就喝一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该是第一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 总之干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没什么好庆祝的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就图个气氛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:00.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,植物园大道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个样子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:21.37,setting,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,68)}植物园
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个样子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是知道才叫我来的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…来照个相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也只是入口而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要照好多纪念照片的那种人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话我本来以为会被拒绝的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是既然来了我就真的超在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是打算来约会的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真意外你竟然这么能出汗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只要离开花店一步感觉就好起来了的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个混蛋凶灵 怎么就那么栩栩如生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先坐那个东西 从空中看一遍游乐园全景怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我推荐的项目在对面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么 那就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一上来就玩这个么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是夏天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先坐点更梦幻些的东西再慢慢降温不好么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是樱花的怨灵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是内容的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道叶月君你是胆小鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说我有点烦恐怖的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试在入口那边看到的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一脸臭屁的鸭子形便盆类似物怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请叫那东西天鹅船好么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来那是天鹅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然去玩一下刚才看到的海贼船？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还挺凉快的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:10.72,SETTING2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz306.39\pos(586,93)}园内导游地图
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹殿堂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚 良缘 植物园之神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 能看见天空树呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边也去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就等人少了再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算高哦完全没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候还没这种东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福之桥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要回头直接走完的话就能实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你叫我了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道这座桥的设定么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:07:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鲤鱼 你看 鲤鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大一条呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:10.59,SETTING3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(477,349)}植 物 园
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头两次就算抵消了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 要怎么让她露出那种笑容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算手牵手走 也完全没有会发生什么的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说了是约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会难道不该是兴高采烈的事么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 想抽烟？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会 现在还好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用介意我哦 那边有吸烟区吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不用 吸烟挺浪费时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间还很长嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:58.69,setting4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(585,239)}可燃垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就不懂就算只是一小会儿也不想分开什么的么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得这…跟想象中的不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是年龄的问题么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是她经常来植物园玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对不对 烟还是先别抽了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不够魄力才对 得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 我在下面看着就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个去坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来干嘛的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被刚才的海贼船吓到了么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那个？好不容易来一趟的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来感受气氛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了去吧 我在下面等你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去玩下一个吧 下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里看着就行 你们两个去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不这么说 我也打算把你留在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的耳环 亮闪闪的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作日人就少了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西 除了我们没人坐了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耀眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视野真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能…能坐你旁边不类…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:39.45,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：「りんか」是日本爱知等地的方言词尾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不类？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重心会倾斜的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 不类？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来有这么高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 人群就像尘埃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴鲁斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:57.20,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：出自吉卜力动画《天空之城》 「巴鲁斯」是播放《天空之城》必念的毁灭咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会毁灭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会活得很久 这就是年纪小的好处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在介意好处什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个当然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不用在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会比店长您活得更长哦 虽然有点对不住您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青菜汁什么的我也每天都喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你很顽强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说我有毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是果然 以后的事还是不清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用现在就说的那么确定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会不清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被异性追求的感觉很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大年龄还是会这么飘飘然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来应该在奇迹殿堂许愿才对的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:38.41,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：叶月说的是bravo 店长只听到前面两个音就成了bra
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真理注定未来是看不透的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也就是说店长也有可能对我倾心是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是死不放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牵着手说话更能传情达意 好像有人这么唱过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说 真是被年轻的气魄压倒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装看开一切可是犯规的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:12:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 喜欢这双粗糙的手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳动者的手 有股向阳的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…叶月君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样太狡猾了 我会困扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是并不讨厌吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么今天变得这么强势？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为幽灵不在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来这样说话 是真的更容易传情达意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟字面意思一样 对方的心思尽在掌握之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想趁他不在的时候赶紧下手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长您对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空之旅 辛苦各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再坐一回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天在那里面太热了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是正在美好的旅行中么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天最好是要纳凉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.68,0:12:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去鬼屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些只会吓人一无是处的家伙 我可不想见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里面很凉快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月君你要是不去的话我就自己去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么办啊 我要进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 我在这里等您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然这么顽固
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您请自便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您居然没有一丝犹豫丢下我就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么进来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就那样在外面等的话也太难看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我丈夫一直是那样的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转圈的太高的 太快的都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话…没必要来游乐场吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你邀我来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为从美惠小姐那里听说了什么吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:13:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然说要三个人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这个原因么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样做是不是心眼很坏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.15,0:14:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算记忆被覆盖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不代表会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是哭哭啼啼也于事无补
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心口不一全写您脸上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易结了婚 却不得不抛下年轻的她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在才开始同情幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长的眼泪掉到我心里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.39,0:14:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要什么口味的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色夏威夷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.52,0:14:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:14:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要道歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然还是…对岛尾君…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就算您说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会退缩的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只是我的骄傲自大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有想过让您选择哪一边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刚才 我知道叶月君你选了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒是 当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的主张一直都只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早在打工之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来这家店的次数就多到让人想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次和你说话的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个会开花么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会开一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:16:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天回去的路上 我蹦了三次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也早做好准备跟那个讨厌的幽灵奉陪到底了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身体…能借给我么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有生命的我能为了喜欢的人做的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长…你能…和我上床么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你什么意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 她看我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好直截了当啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…你问得这么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.76,0:16:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然不可能答应啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经玩够了么 游乐设施？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想玩好多种么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以随便玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.51,0:17:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…要不要到店里来坐坐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开店前的流程我还没有告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始么 明明是休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间还早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在记住比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了店长好我最应该做的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才该谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游乐场之类的 如果没有契机的话我也不会怎么去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧 我给你泡茶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去买包烟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在二楼 你到时候直接上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇晃晃的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝醉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 今天真是尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可还是没点眉目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 没点眉目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我身体的事呢 现在愿意了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 借给你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是你说的啊 不能反悔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真是个老掉牙的奇迹梗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借酒消愁的人真是悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不用幽灵来可怜我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热死了 好刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了好刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了在楼上等你么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.05,0:19:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅子海苔茶和香料奶茶要哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别坐在那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 一身酒气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚去喝酒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那家伙喝酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 店长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫店长啊 总觉得有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很怪唉 叫你店长什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 突然间说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喝香料奶茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能听到了呢 我的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以摸到你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个醉鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以摸到你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的你个醉鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把它脱了我去拿换的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:20:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点擦一擦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月君？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是活着的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.85,0:21:30.79,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつも夢の中では あなたは笑ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.85,0:21:30.79,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦中的你永远是笑着的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:38.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうして ねえ 消えないの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:38.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何不曾消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:40.46,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I gave you everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:40.46,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给了你一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:42.23,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You gave me anything？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:42.23,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给了我什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.33,0:21:45.76,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっといつまででも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.33,0:21:45.76,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是永恒不变的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:47.15,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:47.15,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.15,0:21:48.94,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still my everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.15,0:21:48.94,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.94,0:21:52.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛してるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.94,0:21:52.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:58.70,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夏に降った 雪のような
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:58.70,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正如盛夏里飘落的雪花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:04.22,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それは儚い奇跡なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:04.22,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个易碎的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:05.86,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かまわない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:05.86,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:11.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたに出会わなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:11.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是没有遇见你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:18.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こんなに切なくて 胸を締め付ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:18.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心也不会如此绞痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:22.31,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こともなかったそれでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:22.31,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:28.00,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたに出会えなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:28.00,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是没能遇见你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:34.86,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強さも優しさも 知らずにいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:34.86,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也就无法领悟强大与温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:43.96,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目を閉じればすぐそこに あなたがいる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:43.96,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上眼你就在离我那么近的地方
